What’s A Social
Wellness Club?

There’s more to health than fitness. While you’ll find a ton of new ways to get active, like AntiGravity Fitness, barre, and HIIT, you’ll get so much more than that.

Enjoy contemporary food and drink at the Catalyst Restaurant & Lounge, connect with friends in our social lounge, or quiet your mind in a meditation pod. Altea Active is here for all of you.

FOR
STRENGTH

Find HIIT, cardio, boxing, strength training, group cycle, Activate small group training, barre and more.

FOR
BALANCE

Try our Himalayan salt lounge, KLAFS Polaris ice room and Sanarium, Float Fit, AntiGravity Fitness, meditation pod, and more.

FOR
COMMUNITY

Be part of the Altea fam. Members have access to our Catalyst Restaurant & Lounge, Starbucks, The Smoothie Bar, Topgolf Swing Suites, duckpin bowling and more.
